text: The 1913 TCU Horned Frogs football team represented Texas Christian University (TCU) in the 1911 college football season. The Horned Frogs finished the season 3–1–2 overall. The team was coached by Fred Cahoon in his first and only year as head coach. The Frogs played their home games in Fort Worth, Texas. ==Schedule== ==References== TCU Category:TCU Horned Frogs football seasons TCU Horned Frogs football
